        public DifferentialDrivetrain​(DrivetrainBase.DrivetrainConfig config,
                              SpeedControllerGroup leftController,
                              SpeedControllerGroup rightController)
        Constructs a new DifferentialDrivetrain with the provided SpeedControllerGroups. It is recommended to make your subclass a singleton with a private constructor.
        Parameters:
        config - The configuration for this drivetrain.
        leftController - The left SpeedControllerGroup for this DifferentialDrivetrain.
        rightController - The right SpeedControllerGroup for this DifferentialDrivetrain.

    • Method Detail

      • setOpenLoop

        public void setOpenLoop​(double left,
                        double right)
        Sets drivetrain speeds in open loop (% of max voltage). This method also clamps input to [-1, 1].
        Parameters:
        left - Percent output of motors on left side of drivetrain
        right - Percent output of motors on right side of drivetrain
